<%- partial('_partials/head/head') %>
<% var layoutClass = 'layout-' + String(page.layout || 'page').replace(/[^a-z0-9_-]+/giu, '-').toLowerCase(); %>
<body class="<%= layoutClass %>">
    <div id="container">
        <a class="skip-link" href="#main"><%= __('nav.skip') %></a>
        <%- partial('_partials/header') %>
        <%- wikiflow_inject('header') %>
        <div class="outer">
            <section id="main" tabindex="-1"><%- body %></section>
            <% if (page.layout !== 'embed' && theme.sidebar && theme.sidebar.position) { %>
                <%- partial('_partials/sidebar') %>
                <%- wikiflow_inject('sidebar') %>
            <% } %>
            <% if (page.layout !== 'embed' && theme.profile && theme.profile.enabled) { %>
                <%- partial('_partials/profile', null, {cache: !config.relative_link}) %>
            <% } %>
        </div>
        <%- wikiflow_inject('footer') %>
        <%- partial('_partials/footer', null, {cache: !config.relative_link}) %>
        <%- partial('_scripts/index') %>
    </div>
    <%- wikiflow_inject('bodyEnd') %>
</body>
</html>
